          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-burch-revealbot"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Bürch has rolled out updates that truly stand out. One key feature is its AI-driven budget optimization—imagine letting the platform automatically allocate your ad spend to the best-performing campaigns without you lifting a finger. Then there's the enhanced reporting suite, which gives you real-time insights across Facebook, Google, and Instagram in a single view. You also get advanced automated rules: set conditions like 'pause ads if cost per lead exceeds $10,' and Bürch executes it instantly. These features aren't just add-ons; they're game-changers for scaling ads. Learn how to use them in our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "step-by-step tutorial",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
