      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l4",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/burch-revealbot-tips"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "At its core, Bürch automates repetitive tasks. You connect your ad accounts—Facebook, Google, Instagram—and set up rules or let the AI handle optimization. For instance, if a campaign is underperforming, Bürch can automatically pause it or shift budget to winners. The platform's intuitive dashboard means you spend less time on manual checks and more time on strategy. It's like having a dedicated assistant that never sleeps. For tips on maximizing this, see our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "best practices",
            "marks": [
              "l4"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
