        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you're looking to save hours each week and boost your ad ROI, Bürch is the tool to try. The combination of automated rules, AI insights, and easy reporting makes it a standout choice for modern marketers. Don't just take my word for it—",
